verbose_text: Compared to the control group, after suppressing the Rho / ROCK pathway with Y-27632 (10 muM), Cav1 expression in EC109 (XREF_FIG), Eca109 (XREF_FIG), TE1 (XREF_FIG), and TE13 (XREF_FIG) cells were all significantly (P < 0.05) inhibited, as was PY14Cav1 expression in TE1 (XREF_FIG) and TE13 (XREF_FIG) cells.
